---
layout: base.njk
title: Essays
navActive: essays
extraCss:
  - pages.css
description: "Essays by Ping-Hsien Lin (Kaniz) — Writing on AI, engineering leadership, fintech, game systems, and lessons from building things."
permalink: /blog/
---

<main class="page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="essays-page__title" data-reveal>Essays</h1>
    <p class="essays-page__desc" data-reveal>Thinking out loud about building software, leading people, and the messy reality of making things that work.</p>

    <div class="essays-list" data-reveal-stagger>
      {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-card__meta">
          <span class="blog-card__date">{{ post.date | formatDate }}</span>
          <span class="blog-card__dot"></span>
          <span class="blog-card__read-time">{{ post.data.readTime }}</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="blog-card__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="blog-card__excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
        <span class="blog-card__category tag">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
